prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, minimalist flat 2D vector art. A humorous and lighthearted scene featuring cartoon-style illustrations of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo. Jordan is shown as a master chef behind a teppanyaki grill, wearing his dark t-shirt. He's laughing as he expertly flips a piece of marbled wagyu steak high in the air with a spatula. Lao Lao, in her white jacket, stands beside him with a gleeful expression, holding up a snowboard as a makeshift platter to catch the flying steak. The snowboard has simple icons of sushi rolls, a Chinese takeout box, and binary code (0s and 1s) scattered across it like stickers. The background is a clean, solid, soft cream color with very minimal abstract shapes suggesting a snowy mountain peak. Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan". The composition is clean, playful, and focuses on the couple's joyful interaction.
